    <title>2022-9-29，Leetcode每日一题</title>
    <link href="https://kimilancet.github.io/2022/09/29/leetcode_19/"/>
    <id>https://kimilancet.github.io/2022/09/29/leetcode_19/</id>
    <published>2022-09-29T12:53:12.316Z</published>
    <updated>2022-09-29T13:56:50.269Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>原题链接：<a href="https://leetcode.cn/problems/remove-nth-node-from-end-of-list/">https://leetcode.cn/problems/remove-nth-node-from-end-of-list/</a></p><h2 id="题目大意"><a href="#题目大意" class="headerlink" title="题目大意"></a>题目大意</h2><p>给你一个链表，删除链表的倒数第n个结点，返回链表。</p><h2 id="思路"><a href="#思路" class="headerlink" title="思路"></a>思路</h2><p>依旧是双指针，都从head出发，一个先走n步，再两指针一起走。</p><h3 id="具体思路（可根据思路画图了解流程）"><a href="#具体思路（可根据思路画图了解流程）" class="headerlink" title="具体思路（可根据思路画图了解流程）"></a>具体思路（可根据思路画图了解流程）</h3><p>假设一个示例链表</p><p>1-&gt;2-&gt;3-&gt;4-&gt;5-&gt;6-&gt;nullstr</p><p>设双指针（front和back），均指向首元结点</p><p>假设n&#x3D;3，这时我们需要删除链表中的结点4</p><p>front指针先走3步，到达链表中结点4的位置（这里front指针恰好指向了结点4，但最终由back指针完成删除，不受影响）</p><p>接下来双指针同时走，直到front指针到达尾结点</p><p>这时双指针都移动了2步，front到达了尾结点6，back指针到达了结点3，也就是目标结点4的前一个结点</p><p>通过删除操作back-&gt;next&#x3D;back-&gt;next-&gt;next;    再返回head即解决。</p><p>设双指针都移动m步，链表长度为size，则<strong>总满足m+n+1&#x3D;size的关系</strong>（front指针走了m+n步，但是是从1开始走，所以需要加1）</p><p>那么由于back指针一共走了m步，所以移动后总会处在距离尾结点n+1的距离，也就是倒数第n+1个结点的位置（目标结点的前一个）</p><p>故上述的删除操作正好删除目标结点。</p><p><strong>注意：若n&#x3D;size，即移除首结点，这时front指针移动到nullstr，返回head-&gt;next即可。</strong></p><h2 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h2><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">Solution</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function">ListNode *<span class="title">removeNthFromEnd</span><span class="params">(ListNode *head, <span class="type">int</span> n)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        ListNode *front = head;<span class="comment">//定义双指针</span></span><br><span class="line">        ListNode *back = head;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; n; i++) &#123;<span class="comment">//移动front指针</span></span><br><span class="line">            front = front-&gt;next;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (front == <span class="literal">nullptr</span>) <span class="keyword">return</span> head-&gt;next;<span class="comment">//移除首结点情况</span></span><br><span class="line">        </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span> (front-&gt;next != <span class="literal">nullptr</span>) &#123;<span class="comment">//当front指针未到尾结点时，双指针前进</span></span><br><span class="line">            front = front-&gt;next;</span><br><span class="line">            back = back-&gt;next;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        back-&gt;next = back-&gt;next-&gt;next;<span class="comment">//退出循环，删除操作</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> head;<span class="comment">//返回head</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
